               <msContents>
                  <summary>Sword of the Trinity, ሰይፈ፡ ሥላሴ፡; Image of the Trinity, መልክአ፡ ሥላሴ፡; Image of Saint George, መልክአ፡ ጊዮርጊስ፡; Image of the Savior of the World, መልክአ፡ መድኃኔ፡ ዓለም፡; Image of Gäbrä Mänfäs Qǝddus, መልክአ፡ ገብረ፡ መንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡; Asmat prayer against the Tongue of People, on how Jacob said it when he fled from the face of his brother, ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡  ልሳነ፡ ሰብእ፡; Asmat prayer Against the Tongue of the People, ልሳነ፡ ሰብእ፡ (በእንተ፡ ልሳነ፡ ዘመድ፡ ወባዕድ፡); Greeting to the Archangel Phanuel as Prayer against the devil; Image of Phanuel, መልክአ፡ ፋኑኤል፡; Image of Mary of Zion, መልክአ፡ ማርያም፡ ጽዮን፡; Image of Mary’s Assumption, መልክአ፡ ፍልሰታ፡ ለማርያም፡; Hymn to Saint George, “I Take Refuge with Thee,” መልክአ፡ ጊዮርጊስ፡ (ተማኅፀንኩ፡); Collection of Asmat prayers against Charm, Ṣälot Bä’ǝntä Śǝray, ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ ሥራይ፡ </summary>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>

                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1"><locus from="1r" to="104v" facs="003">Fols 1r–104v</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2296Sayfas">Sayfa Śǝllāse</title>
                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.1"><locus from="1r" to="6v" facs="003">Fols 1r–6v</locus><title>Portion to be read daily</title></msItem>
                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2"><locus from="7r" to="11r" facs="009">Fols 7r–11r</locus><title>Monday</title></msItem>
                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.3"><locus from="11r" to="11v" facs="013">Fols 11r–11v</locus><title>One Miracle of the Trinity</title></msItem>
                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.4"><locus from="12r" to="15r" facs="014">Fols 12r–15r</locus><title>Tuesday</title></msItem>
                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.5"><locus from="15r" to="15v" facs="017">Fols 15r–15v</locus><title>Two Miracles of the Trinity</title></msItem>
                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.6"><locus from="16r" to="20r" facs="018">Fols 16r–20r</locus><title>Wednesday</title></msItem>
                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.7"><locus from="20r" to="21r" facs="021">Fols 20r–21r</locus><title>Two Miracles of the Trinity</title></msItem>
                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.8"><locus from="21v" to="26r" facs="023">Fols 21v–26r</locus><title>Thursday</title></msItem>
                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.9"><locus from="26r" to="26v" facs="028">Fols 26r–26v</locus><title>One Miracle of the Trinity</title></msItem>
                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.10"><locus from="27r" to="30r" facs="029">Fols 27r–30r</locus><title>Friday</title></msItem>
                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.11"><locus from="31r" to="33r" facs="033">Fols 31r–33r</locus><title>Saturday</title></msItem>
                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.12"><locus from="34v" to="38r" facs="037">Fols 34v–38r</locus><title>Sunday</title></msItem>
                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.13"><locus from="38r" to="39r" facs="040">Fols 38r–39r</locus><title>One Miracle of the Trinity</title></msItem>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2"><locus from="41r" to="47r" facs="043">Fols 41r–47r</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2736RepCh20">Malkǝʾa
                                                  Śǝllāse</title>
                  <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                    ሰላም፡ ለህላዌክሙ፡ ዘይመውዕ፡ ህላዌያተ፡<lb/>
                    ለረኪበ፡ ስሙ፡ ኅቡዕ፡ አመ፡ ወጠንኩ፡ ተምኔተ።<lb/>
                    እምግብርክሙ፡ ሥላሴ፡ ሶበ፡ ረከብኩ፡ አስማተ።<lb/>
                    መለኮተ፡ ለለ፩፡ ዘዘዚአክሙ፡ ገጻተ።<lb/>
                    እንበለ፡ ትድምርት፡ እሰሚ፡ ወእሁብ፡ ትድምርተ፡
                  </incipit>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i3"><locus from="47v" to="53r" facs="050">Fols 47v–53r</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2866RepCh147">Malkǝʾ-hymn to St
                                                  George</title>
                  <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                  ሰላም፡ ለዝክረ፡ ስምከ፡ ዘሰሌዳ፡ ሞገስ፡ መጽሐፉ።<lb/>
                  ዘያሤኒ፡ ኵሎ፡ ወዘያስተሴፉ።<lb/>
                  ጥዑመ፡ ዜና፡ ጊዮርጊስ፡ ለሀሊበ። ዕጎልት፡ ሱታፉ።<lb/>
                  ሰላምከ፡ ወረድኤትከ፡ በላዕሌየ፡ ያዕርፉ።<lb/>
                  አኮ፡ ለምዕር፡ ዳዕሙ፡ ለዝላፉ።
                  </incipit>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i4"><locus from="53r" to="59r" facs="055">Fols 53r–59r</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2883RepCh164">Malkǝʾa madḫāne
                                                  ʿālam</title></msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i5"><locus from="59v" to="67r" facs="062">Fols 59v–67r</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2930RepCh211">Malkǝʾa ʾAbuna
                                                  Takla Hāymānot</title>
                  <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                    ሰላም፡ ለኪ፡ ደብረ፡ ሊባኖስ፡ ገነት። ፄና፡ መዓዛኪ፡ ዕፍረት።
                  </incipit>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i6"><locus from="67v" to="69v" facs="070">Fols 67v–69v</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2915RepCh196">Malkǝʾ-hymn to
                                                  Gabra Manfas Qǝddus</title>
                  <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                    ሰላም፡ ለፅንሰትከ፡ መሠረተ፡ ነገር፡ ወውጣኔ፡<lb/>
                    ወለልደትከ፡ ሰላም፡ በብስራተ፡ መልአክ፡ ሠናየ፡ ቅኔ።<lb/>
                    ገብረ፡ መንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ጳውሎስ፡ ሰባኬ፡ ሃይማኖት፡ ውስተ፡ ኵርጓኔ።<lb/>
                    ተማኅፀንኩ፡ በኪዳንከ፡ ከመ፡ ኢይርአይ፡ ኵነኔ።<lb/>
                    ወበእንተዝ፡ ኃሠሥኩ፡ ኪያከ፡ መድኃኔ።
                  </incipit>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i7"><locus from="71r" to="71v" facs="073">Fols 71r–71v</locus>
                  <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1771Lessan">Asmat prayer against the Tongue of People, on how Jacob said it when he fled from the face of his brother</title>
                  <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                    ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡  ልሳነ፡ ሰብእ፡.
                    በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡<gap reason="omitted"/> ናሁ፡ ንዜንዎክሙ፡ በዘድኅነ፡ ያዕቆብ፡ እምልሳነ፡ ሰብእ፡ ወጐየ፡ ያዕቆብ፡ እምገጸ፡ ኤሳው፡ እኁሁ፡ ወነገደ፡ ምድረ፡ ሶርያ፡<gap reason="omitted"/>
                    </incipit>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i8"><locus from="71v" to="78r" facs="074">Fols 71v–78r</locus>
                  <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3034RepCh314">Asmat prayer Against the Tongue of the People, ልሳነ፡ ሰብእ፡ (በእንተ፡ ልሳነ፡ ዘመድ፡ ወባዕድ፡). </title>
                  <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                    በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡<gap reason="omitted"/>ናሁ፡ ተማኅፀንኩ፡ በኆኅያተ፡ ስምከ፡ ካፍ።
                    ወበቀዳማይ፡ የውጣ፡ ዘጥንተ፡ ፊደሉ፡ አሌፍ።<lb/>
                    ከመ፡ ታድኅነኒ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ እምትንሣኤ፡ ልሳን፡ ወአፍ።<lb/>
                    እስመ፡ ልሳን፡ ቀተሎሙ፡ ለማኅበረ፡ ሰማዕት፡ አዕላፍ።<lb/>
                    በነገረ፡ ውዴት፡ ጽኑዕ፡ ዘይባልሕ፡ እምሰይፍ ፦
                  </incipit>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i9"><locus from="78r" to="78v" facs="080">Fols 78r–78v</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2765RepCh49">Malkǝʾ-hymn (Salām)
                                                  to Phanuel</title>
                  <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                    ሰላም፡ ለከ፡ ሰዳዴ፡ ሰይጣናት፡ ፋኑኤል፡ ለእግዚአብሔር፡ እምጽርሑ።<lb/>
                    ከመ፡ ኢይስክዩ፡ ሰብአ፡ እለ፡ ይኔስሑ።<lb/>
                    በጌጋይ፡ ዘዘዚአሁ።
                  </incipit>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i10"><locus from="80r" to="87v" facs="082">Fols 80r–87v</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2885RepCh166">Malkǝʾa
                                                  Fānuʾel</title>
                  <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                    ሰላም፡ ለዝክረ፡ ስምከ፡ ዘይደልዎ (corrected)፡ ተበፅዖ።<lb/>
                    እምውሉደ፡ ሰብእ፡ ኵሉ፡ በተዚያንዎ፡ ወበተዛውኦ፡<lb/>
                    እስመ፡ ቅድሜሆሙ፡ አንተ፡ ዘትተግህ፡ በተራድኦ።<lb/>
                    ፋኑኤል፡ ስመ፡ ዚአከ፡ ሶበ፡ እወጥን፡ ጸውኦ፡<lb/>
                    ከመ፡ ልማድከ፡ ለፀርየ፡ ፍጡነ፡ ጽብኦ።
                  </incipit>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i11"><locus from="87v" to="89v" facs="090">Fols 87v–89v</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1857Malkea">Malkǝʾa Māryām
                                                  Ṣǝyon</title>
                  <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                    ሰላም፡ ለዝክረ፡ ስምኪ፡ ከመ፡ ኮለ፡ ገዳም፡ ዘይጼኑ።<lb/>
                    ለስእርተ፡ ርእስኪ፡ ሰላም፡ ወለርእስኪ፡ በበዘመኑ።<lb/>
                    ማርያ፡ ጽዮን፡ ለእግዚአብሔር፡ አስከሬኑ።<lb/>
                    መኑ፡ መኑ፡ ዘከማኪ፡ መኑ።<lb/>
                    አምላከ፡ ሰማያዊ፡ ዘፆረ፡ በሕጽኑ።
                  </incipit>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i12"><locus from="89v" to="91r" facs="092">Fols 89v–91r</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2932RepCh213">Malkǝʾa
                                                  fǝlsatā</title>
                  <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                    ሰላም፡ ለፍልሰትኪ፡ ምሳሌ፡ ነፍስኪ፡ ኢመዋቲ።<lb/>
                    በተዕርእዎ፡ አሐቲ።<lb/>
                    ድንግል፡ በ፪ኤ፡ ማርያ፡ ወለተ፡ ማቲ።<lb/>
                    ሐመረ፡ ተርሴስ፡ ዘሰሎሞን፡ አንቲ።<lb/>
                    እንተ፡ አተዉ፡ ጠቢባን፡ ወርቅ፡ ያፌዙ፡ ባቲ፡
                  </incipit>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i13"><locus from="91r" to="95r" facs="093">Fols 91r–95r</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3032RepCh312">Hymn to St
                                                  George</title>
                  <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                    ነገረ፡ ፊደላት፡ ሳምን፡ ከመ፡ ዳንዔል፡ ፈከረ፡<lb/>
                    ናሁ፡ ወጠንኩ፡ ዘውዳሴከ፡ ምሥጢረ።<lb/>
                    ጊዮርጊስ፡ ፍቅርከ፡ አቅመ፡ ረሰየኒ፡ ገብረ፡<lb/>
                    መኑ፡ ይከልዓኒ፡ ዜና፡ ገድልከ፡ ነጊረ።<lb/>
                    እመ፡ አንቀልቅሎ፡ ኢልማድ፡ ነፋሳት፡ አድባረ።
                  </incipit>
                </msItem>
                <msItem xml:id="ms_i14">
                  <locus from="96r" to="170r" facs="098">Fols 96r–170r</locus>
                  <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5888AsmatPrayer"> Collection of Asmat prayers against Charm, Ṣälot Bä’ǝntä Śǝray, ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ ሥራይ፡, (col. 2)</title>
                  <incipit xml:lang="gez">
